Package akka.remote.security.provider

Class DeprecatedAkkaProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.remote.security.provider.DeprecatedAkkaProvider
  • Deprecated. 
    Use SecureRandom instead. We cannot prove that this code is correct, see https://doc.akka.io/docs/akka/current/security/2018-08-29-aes-rng.html. Since 2.5.16.

    public class DeprecatedAkkaProvider
extends java.lang.Object
    A provider that for AES128CounterRNGFast, a cryptographically secure random number generator through SecureRandom
